{"tid":1311033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反修例】路透社︰跛腳鴨林鄭 下台只是時間問題","createTime":"2019-07-13T03:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T04:16:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93c52951899472cd115e3d03a68d35cb940d7a39","tid":1311033,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥(圖)周二發表長篇大論講話，但未能平息民怨，路透社稱，林鄭已由「鐵娘子變成跛腳鴨」(from Iron Lady to lame duck)，指她當日被問及會否下台時，說了一句「行政長官下台不是簡單的事」，有分析認為是「她可能已經呈辭的跡象」(a sign that she may have already tendered her resignation)，但指「北京只會在時機成熟時讓她走」(will only let her go when the time is right)。<br />\n<br />\n報道訪問了本港學者及評論員盧兆興(Sonny Lo)，稱北京或想林鄭留下，修補由修例造成的部分傷害，而不是留給下一任特首處理，但認為幾乎可以肯定她會在明年9月立法會選舉前下台。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【反修例】路透社分析︰跛腳鴨林鄭-下台只是時間問題-180162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%EF%B8%B0%E8%B7%9B%E8%85%B3%E9%B4%A8%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-180162&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWaGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=e70397bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【反修例】路透社分析︰跛腳鴨林鄭-下台只是時間問題-180162</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krnGiC5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrnGiC5.jpg&h=752337c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLuA7wv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLuA7wv.png&h=dbe87cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e96365f17554fdb0554dd533dd7a8b5e44cbb1c2","tid":1311033,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"路透社原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-extradition-lam-analysis/from-iron-lady-to-lame-duck-hong-kong-leaders-departure-seen-as-mere-matter-of-time-idUSKCN1U50IV\" data-sr-url=\"https://